      <li><strong>Work Table:</strong> Stainless steel table for staging dough and collecting finished products.</li>
      <li><strong>Exhaust Hood:</strong> Mandatory for gas-fired equipment. Size it 6 inches wider than your machine on all sides.</li>
      <li><strong>Gas Connection:</strong> Commercial LPG cylinder setup with regulator, or PNG connection.</li>
      <li><strong>Hot Case / Insulated Container:</strong> To hold cooked rotis warm until serving.</li>
      <li><strong>Fire Extinguisher:</strong> Required by FSSAI and fire safety norms for any commercial kitchen using gas.</li>
